    "body": "2019/05/30 - ABOUT THIS GAMEThe 7th installment in the popular SonoHana yuri eroge series. This game introduces a new couple: Suminoe Takako, a young and still inexpert teacher at the elementary department of St. Michael's School for Girls, and one of her students, the daring ojousama Houraisen Runa. Title: A Kiss For The Petals - Sweet Enchanting KissesOriginal title: その花びらにくちづけを あまくてほしくてとろけるちゅうYear: Japanese 2009-12-11, English 2011-11-22Length: Short (2 - 10 hours)Language: EnglishVoice: Japanese18+ SCREENSHOTS~(˘▾˘~)  DOWNLOAD  (~˘▾˘)~Google Drive - Mega. nzSYSTEM REQUIREMENTSMINIMUM:OS: Windows 7 or later"
